Title: DKNY Be Delicious EDT Eau de Toilette  -  50 ml
Description: This edgy fragrance combines the hustle of the city and the purity of nature. With notes of green apple and intoxicating coffee, this scent is masculine to the core.Fresh from New York DKNY Be Delicious Men melds the rare luxuriance of nature with the powerful style of the big city with crisp, wet greens, modern woods, green apples and intoxicating coffee. Masculine to the core, it's a scent for the modern man - dynamic, uplifting, but sensual and full of promises. DKNY Be Delicious Men invites you to take a juicy nibble out of life. Be Delicious Men was launched in 2004, created by perfumers Olivier Gillotin and Pierre Negrin. Be Delicious Men is classified as Woody Aromatic fragrance. DKNY Be Delicious notes consist of top notes of Grapefruit, Green Apple, middle notes of Jasmine, Juniper Berries, Sea Water and base notes of Coffee, Patchouli, Woodsy.
